Interface EnhancedMap

Show UML class diagram
  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Map<String,String>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPropertiesDecorator, CachingProperties, FindableProperties, HelpSupportedProperties, MultipleProperties, ObservableProperties, ReadonlyProperties, ThreadSafeProperties, VectorPrintProperties

    public interface EnhancedMap
extends Map<String,String>, Cloneable, Serializable
    This interface describes map enhancements for typing support, multiple value support, key based help and preparing keys and values before addition.
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
    See Also:
    KeyValueObservable
